  "description": [
    "Shes Angel Of Nursing To Vietnam By Beverly Beepe NHATRANG South Vietnam AP A 25yearold American blonde with the face and figure of a movie starlet is nursing the sick in the shadow of the Vietnam war Marva E Haaselblad New York City has been in this coastal town 186 miles northeast o Saigon since February ait a mission hos pital Fighter planes bombard strafe the nearby jungled hills for Com munist Viet Cong guerrillas and helicopters whirl over her beige colored hospital taking Viet namese troops into the mountains On an artillery range outside the hospital on the edge of the South China Sea guns boom out daily as Vietnamese artillerymen practice She Studied Nursing Graceful Marva is so wrapped up in her work she can say None of this worries me I hardly know that there is a war going on Marva is a Baptist and has com mitted three years of her life for work in Vietnam with the Na tional Protestant Church of Viet nam She has spent much of her life abroad moving from her birth place in St Louis Mo when she was 2 years old to go to India with her surgeon father"
